      • buildPositionIndex

        public void buildPositionIndex(File f)
                        throws IOException
        Indexes references component of the given file. that is experiments, interaction, interactor, feature and participant so that we know where they are in the file and we can jump in the right position should we want to extract one of them.
        Parameters:
        f - the file to index.
        Throws:
        IOException - if any.
